                        annos cum magna diligentia descripsit. Baleus. 
                    </marginalia_text>
                    <person name="Caradocus"/>
                    <!-- NBW: This is Caradoc of Llancarfan, https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Caradoc_of_Llancarfan, atributed author of "A History of Cambria." Most of these attributions to authors come from John Bale's "Scriptoium illustrium maioris britanniae catalogus" and likely from the copy held in ChCh with Dee's annotations (Wb.4.8) -->
